## Description {#details}

Typed tracking ref.

Track refererences of a particular type. It&#39;s useful to use this for <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mdnode">MDNode</a></em> and <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/valueasmetadata">ValueAsMetadata</a></em>.

Definition at line 106 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/trackingmdref-h">TrackingMDRef.h</a>.
